room_title: Escape room "Clue Dunnit?" by The Clue Room in Denver
room_description: Reginald Mortas cordially invites you to attend a most unusual gathering… one that may well alter the course of your very existence. There will be celebration, there will be competition, and there will be peril… for this is one adventure that will require every ounce of your wit and cunning if you wish to emerge victorious. Mortas Mansion awaits you…
